#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pacific Area"
msgstr "Pacifiško območje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a player has finished distributing his armies, he clicks the "
"<guibutton>Valid</guibutton> button to allow the next player to distribute "
"his bonus armies. As for the initial distribution, when all player have "
"placed their armies, they can start a new redistribution cycle or start a "
"new turn…"
msgstr ""
"Ko igralec konča z razdelitvijo svojih vojsk, klikne gumb "
"<guibutton>Veljavno</guibutton>, da omogoči naslednjemu igralcu, da razdeli "
"svoje dodatne vojske. Kar se tiče začetne porazdelitve, ko vsi igralci "
"razporedijo svoje vojske, lahko začnejo nov cikel prerazporeditve ali "
"začnejo novo potezo…"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Referenca ukazov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main &ksirk; window"
msgstr "Glavno okno &ksirk;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid "The buttons"
msgstr "Gumbi"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit Game"
msgstr "Zapusti igro"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "Causes the program to quit."
msgstr "Povzroči konec izvajanja programa."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New Game</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nova igra</phrase>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>New Game</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Nova igra</guibutton>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts a new game. It will cause the displaying of a dialog asking the "
"number of players. After that, each player will be asked its name with "
"another dialog."
msgstr ""
"Začne novo igro. Povzročilo bo prikaz pogovornega okna s vprašanjem o "
"številu igralcev. Po tem bo vsak igralec v drugem pogovornem oknu vprašan za "
"njegovo ime."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid "Developer's Guide to &ksirk;"
msgstr "Vodnik za razvijalce za &ksirk;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please refer to <ulink url=\"https://api.kde.org/\">https://api.kde.org/</"
"ulink> for the documentation of the API. It was quite complete but is "
"currently a little bit outdated. There are no comments in the <literal role="
"\"extension\">.cpp</literal> implementation files."
msgstr ""
"Za dokumentacijo API-ja glejte <ulink url=\"https://api.kde.org/\">https://"
"api.kde.org/</ulink>. Bil je precej popoln, vendar je trenutno nekoliko "
"zastarel. V implementacijskih datotekah <literal role=\"extension\">.cpp</"
"literal> ni komentarjev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that I originally developed this game under &Windows; with "
"<application>Borland C++</application> and <application>WinG</application>. "
"I ported it to &Java; before converting back to C++ and &kde;. At the "
"beginning I used French or a mix of French and English to name the "
"identifiers (classnames, methods, members, &etc;). I also used French for "
"the comments. When I decided to distribute this game, I decided to convert "
"all to english... but I am clearly not a native English speaker: please "
"suggest or make and submit corrections, to the code comments or to this "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da sem to igro prvotno razvil pod &Windows; z "
"<application>Borland C++</application> in <application>WinG</application>. "
"Prenesel sem ga v &Java; pred pretvorbo nazaj v C++ in &kde;. Na začetku sem "
"za poimenovanje identifikatorjev (imena razredov, metod, članov itd.) "
"uporabljal francoščino ali mešanico francoščine in angleščine. Za komentarje "
"sem uporabil tudi francoščino. Ko sem se odločil za distribucijo te igre, "
"sem se odločil, da vse pretvorim v angleščino ... vendar očitno nisem "
"materni govorec angleščine: predlagajte ali naredite in oddajte popravke "
"komentarjev kode ali te dokumentacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating new skins"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje novih preoblek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ksirk; comes with a skin editor, named <command>ksirkskineditor</command>, "
"that allows to edit all skin data, as soon as graphics (map, sprites, &etc;) "
"are available in a &SVG; file. Please see the &i18n-ksirkskineditor; manual "
"for further details."
msgstr ""
"&ksirk; prihaja z urejevalnikom preoblek, imenovanim "
"<command>ksirkskineditor</command>, ki omogoča urejanje vseh podatkov "
"preobleke, takoj ko so grafike (zemljevid, sprite itd.) na voljo v &SVG; "
"datoteki. Oglejte si &i18n-ksirkskineditor; priročnik za več podrobnosti."

